ree under it:\\n\\n```\\nrefs/entire/carry_forward → commit → tree:\\n  <session-id-1>/\\n    src/auth.go     ← agent's blob\\n    src/main.go\\n  <session-id-2>/\\n    lib/utils.py\\n```\\n\\nOn each commit:\\n1. PostCommit compares committed files against blobs in this tree\\n2. Removes completed files/sessions from the tree\\n3. Writes a new commit updating the ref (same in-memory tree-building we already do)\\n4. When tree is empty, delete the ref entirely\\n\\nThe shadow branch during active sessions could also move to this namespace — `refs/entire/shadow/<hash>-<worktree>` — keeping `git branch` completely clean. But that's a separate concern from the carry-forward problem.\\n\\nDoes this feel right, or do you see issues with the `refs/entire/` approach?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1482,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":111628,\"output_tokens\":477,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1482,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYkeR48F55oDY1b381mbG\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"cfc167a5-6406-436f-aab4-ee185678ce14\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T21:30:39.886Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"cfc167a5-6406-436f-aab4-ee185678ce14\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"9b854080-5799-41cb-91c1-a3714b4bb75f\",\"version\":\"2.1.69\",\"gitBranch\":\"main\",\"slug\":\"wild-soaring-treasure\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR}/cmd/entire/main.go hooks claude-code stop\"},\"parentToolUseID\":\"af21cedf-7ce2-4cfa-8746-6d215736e371\",\"toolUseID\":\"af21cedf-7ce2-4cfa-8746-6d215736e371\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T21:3