es affected**: 356, 369-377 (signature), 436-506 (logic), 278-330 (helpers)\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 2. **manual_commit_hooks.go** — Hook Integration Points\\n\\n**Current State**: Three hooks interact with carry-forward:\\n- `PrepareCommitMsg()` (lines 301-478) — adds checkpoint trailer before commit\\n- `PostCommit()` (lines 727-1100+) — detects what was committed\\n- `postCommitProcessSession()` (lines 843-1011) — orchestrates carry-forward\\n\\n**Changes Needed**:\\n\\n#### A. In `PrepareCommitMsg()` (lines 301-478):\\n\\nAdd hunk-level carry-forward detection after line 367 (`filterSessionsWithNewContent`):\\n\\n```go\\n// Line ~370, add new check for hunk-level content\\nif len(sessionsWithContent) > 0 {\\n  // NEW: Load hunk state from refs/entire/carry_forward/<session-id>\\n  hunkState, hunkErr := s.loadCarryForwardHunks(ctx, sessionsWithContent[0].SessionID)\\n  if hunkErr == nil && hunkState != nil {\\n    // Hunk-level carry-forward exists from previous partial commit\\n    // Log for visibility: \\\"Previous commit consumed X of Y hunks\\\"\\n    logging.Debug(logCtx, \\\"prepare-commit-msg: hunk-level carry-forward detected\\\",\\n      slog.String(\\\"session_id\\\", sessionsWithContent[0].SessionID),\\n      slog.Int(\\\"remaining_hunks\\\", len(hunkState.RemainingHunks)),\\n    )\\n    // Trailer is still added—hunk state guides what to condense in PostCommit\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\n#### B. In `postCommitProcessSession()` (lines 843-1011):\\n\\n**Line ~910-916 (filesTouchedBefore capture)**:\\nAdd hunk state capture alongside file list:\\n```go\\nvar filesTouchedBefore []string\\nvar fileHunkStateBefore map[string]*HunkState  // NEW\\nif state.Phase.IsActive() {\\n  filesTouchedBefore = s.resolveFilesTouched(ctx, state)\\n  // NEW: Load hunk-level carry-forward from last checkpoint\\n  fileHunkStateBefore, _ = s.loadCarryForwardHunks(ctx, state.SessionID)\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Line ~967-970 (filesWithRemainingAgentChanges call)**:\\nUpdate call to accept and retur